Package seedu.addressbook.commands

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddCommand
    Adds a person to the address book.
    ClearCommand
    Clears the address book.
    Command
    Represents an executable command.
    CommandResult
    Represents the result of a command execution.
    DeleteCommand
    Deletes a person identified using it's last displayed index from the address book.
    ExitCommand
    Terminates the program.
    FindCommand
    Finds and lists all persons in address book whose name contains any of the argument keywords.
    HelpCommand
    Shows help instructions.
    IncorrectCommand
    Represents an incorrect command.
    ListCommand
    Lists all persons in the address book to the user.
    SortCommand
    Sorts the address book and lists it.
    ViewAllCommand
    Shows all details of the person identified using the last displayed index.
    ViewCommand
    Shows details of the person identified using the last displayed index.
